matrix.matrixComp

Class MatrixComputationSparseDistributed

  • java.lang.Object
    • matrix.matrixComp.MatrixComputationSparse
      • matrix.matrixComp.MatrixComputationSparseDistributed
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MatrixComputation
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    MatrixComputationSparseDistributedDynamic, MatrixComputationSparseDistributedDynamicSorted

    public class MatrixComputationSparseDistributed
extends MatrixComputationSparse
    Provides the implementation for performing arithmetic operations between sparse matrices. All operations are performed in a cluster. It uses an AdapterDistribution as an interface for different middlewares.
    Author:
    Antonela Tommasel
